{
  "texts": [
    "The secondary search terms, also presented in Table 1, included combinations related to \"benign breast lesions treatment,\" \"benign breast lesions diagnosis,\" \"mammography,\" \"breast malignancy,\" \"breast lump,\" \"breast cancer treatment,\" and \"breast cancer diagnosis.\"",
    "A subset of crucial search queries and their combinations were chosen based on their relevance to AI's application in breast cancer diagnosis and treatment research.",
    "We broadened our literature review to encompass combinations of key search terms related to breast cancer, focusing on diagnosis and treatment.",
    "By including criteria for breast cancer and microarray gene expression with terms like artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML), our goal was to investigate how AI and ML are applied in breast cancer research utilizing microarray gene expression data.",
    "This data is crucial for understanding the roles of gene biomarkers in the onset and progression of breast cancer."
  ]
}